text.tspan: Hi! I’m wondering how your product can help Sales
team. Can you help me answer this question?
Hello! Thank you for reaching out! Sure i will
answer your question. Acquire is „simply one
tool to rule them all”.🎯 You can qualify leads
via chat bot, then collect them in CRM 👤 ( of
course it is integrated with Salesforce), 💬
communicate with qualified and potential leads,
and then verify your efforts with analytics 📊
